v 1.0
Simple metronome:
- set frequency with a slider
- start or stop with a button
- frequency can be changed anytime

v 2.0
Programmable metronome:
- two sliders:
	- set starting frequency
	- set frequency of changes
- frequency and frequency of changes
  can be adjusted manually
- frequency is incremented automatically
  based on preset frequency of changes
- use redio buttons to toggle between
  simple (constant) mode and
  programmable (linearly progressive) mode
